/files\/2023\/12\/16-LSMs.pdf\">Land-Surface Models<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uwm.edu\/evans36\/files\/2023\/12\/17-Radiation.pdf\">Radiation Parameterization<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uwm.edu\/evans36\/files\/2023\/12\/18-ModelInit.pdf\">Model Initialization<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uwm.edu\/evans36\/files\/2023\/12\/19-IntrotoDA.pdf\">Introduction to Data Assimilation<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uwm.edu\/evans36\/files\/2023\/12\/20-DAMethods.pdf\">Variational and Kalman Filter Data Assimilation Methods<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uwm.edu\/evans36\/files\/2023\/12\/21-DARTTutorialPart1.pdf\">Introduction to the Ensemble Adjustment Kalman Filter<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uwm.edu\/evans36\/files\/2023\/12\/22-DARTTutorialPart2.pdf\">Multivariate\/Non-Identity Observation Data Assimilation<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uwm.edu\/evans36\/files\/2023\/12\/23-DARTTutorialPart3.pdf\">Sampling Error and Observation Localization<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/sites.uwm.edu\/evans36\/files\/2023\/12\/24-DARTTutorialPart4.pdf\">Other Ensemble Data Assimilation Methods<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Class Resources<\/h3>\n<p>Additional resources can be found at the outset of many of the lecture notes provided above, particularly those related to physical parameterizations.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>NWP Essentials:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.meted.ucar.edu\/training_course.php?id=46\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">MetEd: NWP Essentials<\/a> (free MetEd account required)<\/li>\n<li><strong>Numerical Methods:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/hogback.atmos.colostate.edu\/group\/dave\/at604pdf\/AT604_LaTeX_Book.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">An Introduction to Numerical Modeling of the Atmosphere<\/a><\/li>\n<li><strong>Numerical Modeling:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ecmwf.int\/en\/learning\/education-material\/lecture-notes\" target=\